t.<br/></paragraph><paragraph>The trigger code version your organization is using is out-of-date. Please have your EHR administrators install the current version for complete eCR functioning.<br/></paragraph><paragraph><content styleCode="Bold">"Influenzal acute upper respiratory infection (disorder)" for "Utah Department of Health" </content></paragraph><paragraph>Reporting to this Public Health Agency is based on "Both patient home address and provider facility address"<br/></paragraph><paragraph><content styleCode="Bold">"Infection caused by novel Influenza A virus variant (disorder)" for "Utah Department of Health" </content></paragraph><paragraph>Reporting to this Public Health Agency is based on "Both patient home address and provider facility address"<br/></paragraph><paragraph><content styleCode="Bold">"Disease caused by severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (disorder)" for "Utah Department of Health" </content></paragraph><paragraph>Reporting is required immediately.  Reporting to this Public Health Agency is based on "Both patient home address and provider facility address"<br/></paragraph><paragraph><content>&gt; Public Health Agency Contact Information<br/><br/></content><content>&gt; CDC COVID-19 webpage (<linkHtml href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/index.html">Information only</linkHtml>)<br/><br/></content></paragraph></text><entry typeCode="DRIV"><act classCode="ACT" moodCode="INT"><templateId extension="2014-06-09" root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.20"/><templateId extension="2017-04-01" root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.15.2.3.8"/><id root="a9899836-4e77-4c0f-8388-8b04b732e850"/><code code="304561000" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.96" codeSystemName="SNOMED CT" displayName="Informing health care professional (procedure)"/><text>Your organization electronically submitted an initial case report to determine if reporting to public health is needed for a patient. The eICR was processed with the warning of: outdated eRSD (RCTC) ver